cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.NE, cs.SI 

The paper proposes a new approach for knowledge transfer in deep learning, which is a common topic in machine learning and artificial intelligence. The paper specifically focuses on the design of loss functions and graph-based representations, which are relevant to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), and social and information networks (cs.SI). Among these sub-categories, cs.LG and cs.AI are the most likely as they are directly related to the topic of knowledge transfer in deep learning.
